<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>예약 완료</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl w-full mx-auto">
            
            {{#isSuccess}}
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-10 text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                    <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600"></i>
                </div>
                
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">예약이 완료되었습니다!</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-10">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">{{patientName}}</span>님의 진료 예약이 성공적으로 접수되었습니다.<br/>
                    예약 당일 원무과에서 접수를 진행해주세요.
                </p>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-left space-y-6 border border-slate-100 mb-10">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4 mb-4">예약 상세 정보</h3>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-6 gap-x-12">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="user" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">환자명</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{patientName}}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">진료과 / 전문의</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{deptName}} / {{doctorName}}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">예약 일자</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{reservationDate}}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">예약 시간</div>
                                <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{reservationTime}}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a href="{{mainUrl}}" target="_parent" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
                        메인으로 가기
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/isSuccess}}

            {{^isSuccess}}
            <div class="text-center py-20">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">예약 정보가 없거나 오류가 발생했습니다.</h2>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="inline-block mt-4 px-6 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors">
                    처음으로 돌아가기
                </a>
            </div>
            {{/isSuccess}}
            
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>